BREAKING: Roland Garros has decided not to give two-time champ Maria Sharapova a wildcard into the tournament. 
French Tennis Federation chief said: "There can be a wildcard for the return from injuries - there cannot be a wildcard for the return from doping." Masha was also forced to retire from her R2 match in Rome today due to injury & will no longer receive direct entry to the Wimbledon main draw.
